    "prerequisites": "",
    "syllabus": {
        "zh": "1.\t遊戲企畫製作<br>2.\t電腦動畫概論<br>3.\tC#語言<br>4.\t體感互動(Leap motion、Kinect)<br>5.\t虛擬實境(Virtual Reality、Cardboard)<br>6.\tWeb伺服器的互動<br>7.\t基於TCP/IP協定的聊天實例<br>8.\t用Unity建立網頁遊戲<br>9.\t將Unity遊戲移植到iOS平台<br>10.\t將Unity遊戲移植到Android平台<br>",
        "en": "1.\tPlanning a game<br>2.\tIntroduction to computer animation<br>3.\tC# programming language<br>4.\tAn introduction to the motion sensing interaction<br>5.\tAn introduction to the Virtual Reality<br>6.\tWriting server and network code for your online game<br>7.\tA chat room based on TCP/IP sockets<br>8.\tUse Unity to build web 2d games<br>9.\tPublish a game to the iOS system<br>10.\tPublish a game to the Android system<br>"
